 ** Freddie Jackson, "Here It Is," RCA. Could Jackson be the Michael Bolton of 
black music? Back from a lengthy recording hiatus, Jackson really oversings to 
his heart's content on several cuts."Was It Something" and "How Does It Feel" 
fare well under such treatment, but his overemoting on the love-gone-wrong 
