<HEADLINE>
<P>
BRIEFLY; KATZ IS APPOINTED ASSISTANT DEAN AT LMU 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Rachelle Katz has been named assistant dean of Loyola Marymount University's 
College of Business Administration. 
</P>
<P>
 She succeeds H. Daniel Stage, who is returning to teaching. Katz, a professor 
of finance, has been chairwoman of the finance and computer information systems 
department for nine years. 
</P>
<P>
 She holds degrees from Stanford, Michigan and Purdue universities. 
</P>
