<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWS, TIPS & BARGAINS; TEE TIMES ON DEMAND 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Golfers can now reserve guaranteed tee times at more than 100 public and 
resort golf courses and private clubs that allow outside play in Arizona, 
California, Nevada and Hawaii, up to 60 days in advance, by calling (800) TEE 
TIME in Sherman Oaks.The company hopes to eventually offer reservations 
nationwide.  
</P>
<P>
 Operators help golfers find courses that match their skill levels. The service 
offers golfers the convenience of central booking and has reserved blocks of 
time at the most popular hours on weekends and weekdays, a spokeswoman said. 
Convenience comes with a price: There is a service fee of $3-$5 per player per 
course, plus a $1.95 transaction charge. 
</P>
</TEXT>
