<HEADLINE>
<P>
WANTED: EQUAL TIME 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Enjoyed James Yenckel's "Pet Peeves From the Road" (Jan. 2). How about equal 
time for women (whose pet peeves include:) 
</P>
<P>
 1.Insufficient toilet facilities in airports, plus many other places. 
</P>
<P>
 2. Lack of space on sink counter for two kits (my husband usually wins in my 
house). 
</P>
<P>
 3. Bathroom plugs that will not accommodate a hair blower. 
</P>
<P>
 4. Shower heads that hit you in the head -- there goes the coiffeur. 
</P>
<P>
 5. No place in the bathroom to hang laundry. 
</P>
<P>
 6. Sink plugs that do not stay down so you can wash your face or do laundry. 
</P>
<P>
 DORIS BLADES 
</P>
<P>
 San Diego 
</P>
