<HEADLINE>
<P>
WHY NO ELDERHOSTEL? 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 I was quite excited when I saw "Tours for the Thinking Person" (Jan. 9) in the 
Travel section.But as I read through the articles I was surprised to find no 
mention of the Elderhostel program. This program has hundreds of classes 
attended by thousands of senior citizens (over 60) every year in countries on 
every continent. Certainly it should at least have been mentioned in your 
column for the mature traveler. 
</P>
<P>
 IRIS BELDING 
</P>
<P>
 Claremont 
</P>
