public trust, which was revealed in the discovery of the Watergate conspiracy 
and provoked his resignation to avoid impeachment after appointing a successor 
who agreed to pardon him, exemplifies the degree of success his efforts to 
rewrite history have achieved. You characterize his Administration as 
"pragmatic," not criminal, and label condemnation of his perfidy "old grudges." 
</P>
