<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
February 6, 1994, Sunday, Bulldog Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 8; Column 1; Sports Desk 
</P>
