<P>
MAN HELD IN FATAL 1993 SHOOTING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Ventura police have arrested a suspect in the slaying of a Ventura man who was 
shot and killed last year outside his apartment building. 
</P>
<P>
 Police arrested Garabet Majoubian, 45, of Canoga Park on Friday in the Dec. 20 
shooting of Erasmo Moro, 48, an Italian national.Moro's body was found in the 
carport area of the Scandia Apartments in east Ventura after police and 
firefighters answered reports of gunshots. Moro had been working at a pizza 
shop in Ventura. 
</P>
<P>
 Based on a tip from a woman who knew both men, Ventura detectives focused 
their investigation on Majoubian soon after the shooting, according to a police 
report. It could not be immediately determined where detectives picked up 
Majoubian on Friday, although he was arrested without incident, according to 
the report. 
