PRESIDENT QUAYLE! NOW THAT YOU'VE LOST THE ELECTION, WHERE ARE YOU GOING?' 
COMMERCIAL FOR OUR COMPANY? STOP. LOVED YOUR POTATO CHIP THING. STOP. 
</P>
<P>
 -- DISNEYLAND/WALT DISNEY WORLD 
</P>
