<HEADLINE>
<P>
THE WEEK AHEAD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * PERSHING SQUARE: The public is invited to celebrate the opening today of the 
revitalized "town square," featuring the newest addition to L.A.'s skyline -- a 
125-foot purple bell tower. The free festival will feature circus workshops for 
children, a variety of foods and nonstop entertainment at 5th and Olive streets 
