<HEADLINE>
<P>
COMING MONDAY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A special section called "Shifting Gears" will look at trends and forces 
shaping our work and careers.It will include a look at emerging career 
opportunities on the electronic superhighway and among corporations with 
intensive overseas operations. It also features an examination of the specific 
concerns and aspirations facing different generations of America's work force. 
The section will appear as Part II of Business. 
</P>
