</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Become a part of the virtual classroom. Earn college degrees without ever 
stepping foot inside a classroom. Also, find out about job prospects and why 
today's college students are demanding more than the basics from dormitory 
living. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA020694-0305 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 011040 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
February 6, 1994, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 3; National Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
